Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:12.38,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Será que ainda haveriam crimes se não existisse mais maldade?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:12.38,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Waruginakutemo tsumi wa umaremasu ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.84,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Onde está a resposta? Alguém sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.84,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Kotae wa doko ni kakusarete'ru no somebody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:25.06,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Não desista, pense um pouco mais! Questione! Responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:25.06,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Akiramenaide mou choi kangaete Question! Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:36.53,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Toque seu rosto enquanto estiver na escuridão
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:36.53,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\1a}Kurayami ni ukande'ru sono hoho ni fureru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:48.25,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}E agarre a justiça que ninguém pode abandonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:48.25,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\1a}Daremo ga yuzurenai seigi o idaite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:53.92,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}A resposta sempre esteve aqui! Tudo mundo sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:53.92,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Kotae wa koko ni chanto aru ja nai everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:59.80,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}Mas mesmo com ela, eu sei que muitos corações ainda vão duvidar!\N — Questione! Responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:59.80,OPRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}Sakedo mou hitotsu kokoro ga harenai Question! Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:06.68,OPTL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1}{\fad(0,1000)}E teremos que continuar vivendo com esta tristeza\N — Questione! Responda!
